类 CompilationSampler

  • java.lang.Object

  • 所有已实现的接口:
    ISampler

    public class CompilationSampler
extends AbstractMXBeanSampler
    A sampler using the MXBean interface to access information about the compilation time. The sampler produces a CompilationRecord each time the sample method is called.
    从以下版本开始:
    1.10
    作者:
    Nils Christian Ehmke

        Abstract method used as interface to realize concrete samplers.
        指定者:
        createNewMonitoringRecords 在类中 AbstractMXBeanSampler
        参数:
        timestamp - the current time.
        hostname - the hostname of the machine where this measurement is performed
        vmName - name of the vm
        monitoringCtr - monitoring controller used in the measurement
        返回:
        returns an array of records containing the measurement
